OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNetflix and Microsoft team 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fup for cheaper plan with   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fadverts                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Netflix has teamed up with Microsoft to
OL,6, offer a cheaper subscription plan to   
OL,7, customers that will show adverts.      
OL,9,FThe streaming giant says the service   
OL,10,Fwill be an "addition" to its existing  
OL,11,Fplans, which do not include adverts.   
OL,13,FThe company has not yet revealed how   
OL,14,Fmuch it plans to charge subscribers for
OL,15,Fthe new service.                       
OL,17,FNetflix announced the move after it    
OL,18,Freported its first subscriber loss in  
OL,19,Fmore than a decade and cut hundreds of 
OL,20,Fjobs earlier this year.                
